[Qin Manor]

370
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,100
[Vice Admiral of Imperial Guard: Wang Yan]
[General of Wu Imperial Guard: Dong Daofu]

371
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:33,400
Greetings to Right Prime Minister Qin and Left Prime Minister Li.

372
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:36,100
We're all on the same side. No need for unnecessary courtesies.

373
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:37,900
Hurry and come forward.

374
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:46,600
Today… we invited General Dong and General Wang over

375
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:49,200
for the north expedition.

376
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:52,300
Although His Majesty issued an official imperial edict on the north expedition,

377
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:55,800
there is more and more ample confidence in the expedition.

378
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,200
The courtiers have had enough of

379
00:30:58,200 --> 00:31:00,400
the days of humiliation and paying tributes.

380
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:03,500
The north expedition is just a matter of time.

381
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,300
The two of you

382
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:10,700
are the most honorable Generals in the Wu Dynasty.

383
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:17,000
The north expedition will be led by you two.

384
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,300
Right Prime Minister Qin, we're flattered.

385
00:31:19,300 --> 00:31:23,000
I... will not let down the great trust of you both.

386
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:26,500
Now, the strength of Jing and Liang is greatly weakened.

387
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:28,700
There is no need for much thinking. You just need to fight.

388
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:31,300
Moreover, our troops are equipped with firearms.

389
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:33,400
We are with strengthened power.

390
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:36,800
I'll appoint Wang Bing and Yang Shike, the Two Generals,

391
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:39,600
to march along the Xizhou and Qizhou border to the north.

392
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:42,100
They'll go directly to Jing's hinterland.

393
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:45,200
You two will lead a group of cavalries respectively.

394
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:47,200
From the trading route between

395
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,800
our country, Wu and Liang,

396
00:31:48,800 --> 00:31:51,900
you will attack from both sides striking the unprepared enemy.

397
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:55,400
This way we will fight and win the series of battles

398
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,500
taking down the capital of Jing.

399
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:59,000
Ingenious!

400
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,800
Give me 2,000 soldiers and horses and 1,000 cavalries.

401
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,979
We will change horses day and night.

402
00:32:02,979 --> 00:32:05,780
I promise that we'll overturn his military camp

403
00:32:05,780 --> 00:32:07,740
when the king of Jing is sleeping.

404
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:10,740
Good!

405
