[He Manor]

429
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:48,700
It'll not be that easy to march north.

430
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,600
A honeymoon trip?

431
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:58,400
Yes! A honeymoon trip.

432
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:02,200
Counting the days, Tan'er and I have been married for a period of time already.

433
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:05,000
Recently due to being busy with work, we weren't able to consider it.

434
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:07,600
Now everything has gone back on track.

435
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:11,000
It's time for us to also have a good rest.

436
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,100
My dear, what do you think?

437
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:15,500
Anyway, you are always the one taking care of these kinds of matters.

438
00:34:15,500 --> 00:34:18,300
Xiao Chan and I will listen to you.

439
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:27,800
A honeymoon trip is usually just for the two of us.

440
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:31,800
You... bringing a child with us would be quite inconvenient.

441
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,600
Xiao Chan has always accompanied me.

442
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:38,000
Without her, I will truly have inconvenience.

443
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:46,500
Forget it.

444
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:49,000
Since you are not willing, then I won't force you to it.

445
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:52,600
- Yes. Yes.
- If Xiao Chan doesn't go, I won't, either.

446
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:57,600
Come on, Tan'er.

447
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:59,600
I was just kidding with you.

448
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:03,200
Actually, I also think I am careless.

449
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:05,400
This way it just so happens that Xiao Chan can care for you.

450
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,400
Take her with us.

451
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,800
- That'll be perfect.
- Yes, perfect.

452
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,800
Young Master and My Lady, don't worry.

453
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,900
I will take good care of you.

454
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,800
Young Master and My Lady.

455
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:16,800
I, Guard Geng, will take good care of you, too.

456
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:25,100
Lao Geng, did we speak to you?

457
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:28,400
Xiao Chan can take care of Tan'er if she goes.

458
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:30,600
Who are you taking care of if you go?

459
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:32,000
Young Master, what are you saying?

460
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:35,000
I, as the chief guard of the Su Family,

461
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:38,800
I would be protecting your personal safety if I go.

462
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:47,600
What's wrong?

463
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:52,100
Lao Geng, the most important thing as a person is honesty.

464
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:57,200
Know yourself clearly and what you can and can't do.

465
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:58,800
Protect us?

466
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:01,600
Please look down at your belly.

467
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:04,300
Anyhow, you are our Su Family's chief guard.

468
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:06,500
Can't you go exercise?

469
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:08,000
Go out for a run.

470
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,200
Lose some weight.

471
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:12,100
When you stand at the entrance of the manor, those that know will say

472
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,800
you are the chief guard of Su Family.

473
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:17,400
Those who don't know would think that you are the Su Family's Chief Divine Altar Cleanser. (Title that was given to Zhu Ba Jian(Pigsy) in the Journey to the West)

474
00:36:18,700 --> 00:36:20,000
That's wrong.

475
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:23,200
What the Elder Master took a liking to wasn't my figure,

476
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:25,300
but my professional skill.

477
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:28,000
Professional skill?

478
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:32,400
I dare ask Young Master how long will you spend on the trip?

479
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:34,200
What's the scenery along the way like?

480
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:36,700
Where is your final endpoint?

481
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,400
Does anyone care about that?

482
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,800
We are going out to have fun.

483
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:46,600
We will just go wherever we walk to while going south.

484
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:50,300
Even if we go to the south, there are different ways of walking.

485
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:07,200
Look, everyone.

486
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:11,300
If we go in the southeast direction, we'll pass by Qiusha and Zhangze.

487
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:13,400
There we can admire the beauty of flowers along the river.

488
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,300
However, it's not flowering season now.

489
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:17,600
Along the road, we will only see faded flowers and withered willows.

490
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:19,700
It's not recommended.

491
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:22,600
If we go in the southwest direction, it'll be a public road.

492
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:24,800
We'll pass by the Anmo and Bi County.

493
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,400
Not only is the road bumpy and muddy,

494
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:28,700
but the destination is also the barren Gobi Desert.

495
00:37:28,700 --> 00:37:30,500
It's uncertain whether we can come back alive.

496
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,400
I don't recommend it even more.

497
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:35,100
Only if we go in the straight south direction

498
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:37,600
will we see a trade route continuously stretching about 150 kilometers.

499
00:37:37,600 --> 00:37:41,100
We will pass by the famous cities of the Wu Dynasty.

500
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,600
Not only is the scenery beautiful,

501
00:37:42,600 --> 00:37:44,600
but we can also eat hawthorn juice,

502
00:37:44,600 --> 00:37:47,600
the glutinous wine lees rice balls, Osmanthus cake and more of these delicacies.

503
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:49,800
There are too many to count.

504
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:54,100
Finally, we arrive at our destination after we climb over a small hill.

505
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:59,000
Lin'an City.

506
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:01,400
Lin'an City?

507
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:06,500
Lin'an City is one of the richest cities in the Wu Dynasty.

508
00:38:06,500 --> 00:38:09,900
Countless merchants come and go with clusters of poets and writers in the city.

509
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:16,800
Among the 100 old cities of the Wu Dynasty, it is the one city that is a must-visit for traveling.

510
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:29,400
Lao Geng,

511
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:33,200
why do you know so much?

512
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:35,300
Young Master, I'm flattered.

513
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:39,000
When I was young, the world was my home

514
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:42,200
